form.text: A new term referring to us modern people living in an economic society (savings, consumption, loans, supply) who interact closely with money. Homo Economicus is used as the name of most of humankind, and it's a word that includes the term “economics.” That expresses humans’ close relationship with economics.
Homo Economicus - tends to make logical choices
